## compositor
exec --no-startup-id "picom"

## autolock
exec --no-startup-id "light-locker"

## bar
exec --no-startup-id "polybar mybar"

# style

## gaps
gaps inner 8
smart_gaps on

## border
set $f_color #e5e5e5
